name: #TeamInsanity
description: This is thee official #TeamInsanity Shirt. We have officially lost our minds to follow Christ. In the word of God it states that we must put off the old and put on the new Ephesians 4:24. Our old way of thinking is our mind of carnality. Which is the way of the flesh. We must renew our minds Romans 12:2 and continue putting on the mind of Christ which means totally coming out of yourself. We must remember two things while being part of team insanity. One Gods thoughts are not our thoughts Isaiah 55:8 and two the mind of carnality can never receive the things of the spirit 1 Corinthians 2:14. With that being said we welcome you into #TEAMINSANITY!
